│ represented as a reduction, it is always safe to vectorize them. However, this is only     │
│ true if the operations are free of side effects and do not have control-flow-like behavior │
│ that can mask `poison`. The `select` instruction is the culprit here; it behaves like a    │
│ `?:` operator, evaluating only one of its \"value\" operands based on the condition. When  │
